topic.body:
Has anyone gotten ZN to work with a Caddy proxy?  I want to access it from a subdomain without specifying a port in the address bar. My caddyfile looks like: 

sub.domain.tld {
  proxy / localhost:43110 {
    header_upstream Host {host}
  }
  proxy /Websockets localhost:43110 {
    websocket
  }
}

I just get the error "Connection with UiServer Websocket was lost. Reconnecting..."  Any suggestions?
